des:
Ketnet Hits (VRT) is a non-stop radio with music for kids.

To start listening, just say "Alexa, open Ketnet Hits" or "Alexa, start Ketnet Hits". At anytime, you can stop listening to ketnet Hits by saying "Alexa, stop".
